<div><div class="related-post clearfix view view-article-single view-id-article_single view-display-id-article_body js-view-dom-id-ffba01e114faf95956fafd446f334023ce684fe641c1b6502740127b32d0de46">
<div class="view-content">
<div class="views-row">
<div class="intro part-left full-width-col-mobile">
<p>RSF figures show that at least four media workers have been killed in Afghanistan so far this year.</p>
<div class="views-element-container"><div class="related-news clearfix view view-article-single view-id-article_single view-display-id-related_stories_main js-view-dom-id-b67e61853e5eaadcdb647315c7eda3c8c83adda09d2d1b6e64aa3f024b0bed83">
<div class="view-header">
<h3 class="views-label views-label-nothing red uppercase-txt">Related News</h3>
</div>
<div class="view-content">
<div>
<ul class="item-list">
<li><a href="/web/20190419131844/https://www.tolonews.com/afghanistan/suspects-sentenced-death-killing-journalist-kandahar">Suspects Sentenced To Death For Killing Journalist In Kandahar<i class="fa fa-angle-right red"></i></a></li>
<li><a href="/web/20190419131844/https://www.tolonews.com/afghanistan/fallen-journalists-remembered-herat-exhibition">Fallen Journalists Remembered At Herat Exhibition<i class="fa fa-angle-right red"></i></a></li>
</ul>
